name: Public-Safety

name: Law-Enforcement-Agency

name: Law-Enforcemen-tOfficer

name: Transportation-Safety

name: Vehicle

name: Brand

description: A factory where vehicles are assembled

name: Engine

name: Fuel

name: Alcohol-Fuel

name: Petroleum-Fuel
description: Fuel derived from crude oil

name: Safety-Agency
description: An organization responsible for ensuring public safety

name: First-Responder

description: A person trained to put out fires
